 golfer\n*  1952   &ndash; [[Nevada Barr]], American actress and author\n*  1952   &ndash; [[Leigh Matthews]], Australian footballer, coach, and sportscaster\n*  1952   &ndash; [[Jerri Nielsen]], American physician and explorer (d. 2009)\n*  1952   &ndash; [[Martin O'Neill]], Northern Irish footballer and manager\n*[[1953]] &ndash; [[Sinan \u00c7etin]], Turkish actor, director, and producer\n*  1953   &ndash; [[Carlos Queiroz]], Portuguese footballer and manager\n*[[1954]] &ndash; [[Catherine Bach]], American actress\n*  1954   &ndash; [[Ron Howard]], American actor, director, and producer\n*  1954   &ndash; [[Rod Reddy]], Australian rugby league player and coach\n*[[1956]] &ndash; [[Tim Daly]], American actor, director, and producer\n*  1956   &ndash; [[Dalia Grybauskait\u0117]], Lithuanian politician, 6th [[President of Lithuania]]\n*[[1958]] &ndash; [[Nik Kershaw]], English singer-songwriter, guitarist, and producer\n*  1958   &ndash; [[Wayne B. Phillips]], Australian cricketer and coach\n*[[1959]] &ndash; [[Nick Griffin]], English politician\n*[[1961]] &ndash; [[Mike Rozier]], American football player\n*[[1962]] &ndash; [[Russell Coutts]], New Zealand sailor\n*  1962   &ndash; [[Mark Gardner (baseball)|Mark Gardner]], American baseball player\n*  1962   &ndash; [[Bill Leen]], American bass player and producer\n*[[1963]] &ndash; [[Bryan Batt]], American actor and singer\n*  1963   &ndash; [[Maurice Benard]], American actor\n*  1963   &ndash; [[Ron Francis]], Canadian ice hockey player and manager\n*[[1964]] &ndash; [[Clinton Gregory]], American singer-songwriter and fiddler\n*  1964   &ndash; [[Paul Le Guen]], French footballer and manager\n*[[1965]] &ndash; [[Booker T (wrestler)|Booker T]], American wrestler and sportscaster\n*  1965   &ndash; [[Stewart Elliott]], Canadian jockey\n*[[1966]] &ndash; [[Paul Hollywood]], English chef\n*  1966   &ndash; [[Zack Snyder]], American director, producer, and screenwriter\n*[[1967]] &ndash; [[George Eads]], American actor\